sentences.english: But the elements of that economic model are universal in character.
sentences.chinese: 但是这种经济模式的组成要素是放诸四海而皆准的。

sentences.english: One of the Four Auspicious Animals. It can stop the evil things and improve the environment.
sentences.chinese: 为吉祥四瑞兽之一，其功效能挡蔽诸煞，改善风水。

sentences.english: Remove ambition and the essential elements of society seem to fly apart .
sentences.chinese: 没有雄心，组成社会的诸要素就会分散开来。

sentences.english: Conclusion The characteristics of P300 of patients with AD deserve further studies.
sentences.chinese: 结论AD患者P300变化诸特点值得进一步随访。

sentences.english: You see, these Bodhisattvas Mahasattvas are able to obtain great benefit.
sentences.chinese: 汝观彼诸菩萨摩诃萨，善获利益。

sentences.english: Their number incalculable; Thus also is the assembly of Bodhisattvas.
sentences.chinese: 非是算数之所能知，诸菩萨众，亦复如是。

sentences.english: A man of business may talk of philosophy, a man who has none may practice it.
sentences.chinese: 商人也许会谈谈哲学，而一无所有者也许会施诸实践。

sentences.english: When the gods wish to punish us, we must first make our prayers.
sentences.chinese: 若诸神要惩罚我等，必先让我等如愿以偿。

sentences.english: You are following the Action Principles.
sentences.chinese: 你正遵循诸行动原则而行事。

sentences.english: One of the Four Auspicious Animals. It can stop evil things and improve your faculty of memory.
sentences.chinese: 吉祥四瑞兽之一，其功效能档蔽诸煞，改善记忆。

sentences.english: These resulted from the gradual intensification of imperial power starting from the middle period of Song Dynasty.
sentences.chinese: 诸如此者，皆与皇权自刘宋中叶以降渐趋强化有关。

sentences.english: Because he can accomplish such good roots.
The Buddha's awesome spirit caused all the realms to unite into a single realm.
sentences.chinese: 一时开现佛之威神，令诸世界合成一界。

sentences.english: The factors of influence on the polarographic determination were investigated and discussed in detail.
sentences.chinese: 对影响白蛋白测定的诸因素作了详细研究和讨论。

sentences.english: However, the environment has changed dramatically since last October.
sentences.chinese: 但是，今天的环境，较诸去年十月已大不相同。

sentences.english: Jesus, to Thee be all glory given;
sentences.chinese: 天人诸荣耀完全归主一身。
